\f0\fs24 \cf0 # Acquisition Strategy Template\
\
Here is a clean, agency-ready Acquisition Strategy Template, suitable for IT, professional services, or agile acquisitions. It reflects guidance from FAR Part 7.1, aligns with best practices from agencies like DHS, DoD, and GSA, and is tailored for both traditional and adaptive acquisition environments.\
