## 10. Risk Management\
\
| Risk                         | Mitigation                                  |\
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------|\
| Team turnover                | Require transition and knowledge sharing     |\
| Schedule slippage            | Use 2-week sprints, track velocity           |\
| Vendor underperformance      | Tie payment to iteration acceptance/QASP     |\
| Lock-in to proprietary systems | Require modular, open-source components   |\
